    <stitle>FRONT STEER AXLE: EATON EFA-12 - CLEAN</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="clean" graphiccount="0">
        <title>CLEAN</title>
        <para>After disassembly and before attempting inspection, clean parts as follows:</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Wash steel parts with ground or polished surfaces in suitable cleaning solvent. Rinse
                thoroughly to remove cleaning solution. Dry parts with clean rags.
            </para>
            <specpara>
                <warning>
                    <para>Gasoline is not an acceptable cleaning solvent because of its extreme combustibility. It is
                        unsafe in the workshop environment.
                    </para>
                </warning>
            </specpara>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Wire brush or steam-clean castings, forgings and other rough surface parts that are
                susceptible to accumulation of mud, road dirt, salt, etc.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
